718538f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 107th Street
718538f-a.text:
Central Park West, west side, at 107th street, from Central Park.

The apartment house at the left is the Lascala.

October 23, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.
718538f-a.folder: Central Park West & 107th Street, Manhattan, NY

718542f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 107th Street
718542f-a.text:
Central Park West, west side, from 107th to 110th Streets. In the centre background may be seen a portion of the Cathedral of St. John the Divine (Protestant Episcopal).
October 23, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.

718541f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 107th Street
718541f-a.text:
Central Park West, 108th to 107th
Streets.  (Before reconstruction).
President borough of Manhattan.
